## Implementation Roadmap

### **Month 1-2: SovereignGuard Foundation**
```bash
# Install Hashicorp Vault
helm install vault hashicorp/vault --namespace security

# Configure YubiKey HSM
ykman oath accounts add "vault-unseal-key-1"

# Set up TPM 2.0 sealing
tpm2_createprimary -C o -g sha256 -G rsa -c primary.ctx
tpm2_create -C primary.ctx -g sha256 -G keyedhash -r sealed.priv -u sealed.pub -i secret.txt
```

### **Month 3-4: Service Mesh Deployment**
```bash
# Install Linkerd
linkerd install | kubectl apply -f -

# Configure mTLS for all services
linkerd inject deployment.yaml | kubectl apply -f -

# Set up NetworkPolicies
kubectl apply -f network-policies/deny-all-default.yaml
```

### **Month 5-6: Financial Enclave**
```python
# Microsoft SEAL homomorphic encryption
import seal

parms = seal.EncryptionParameters(seal.scheme_type.ckks)
# Configure secure enclave for SwarmGate
# Trading logic executes on encrypted portfolio values
```

### **Month 7-8: Air-Gapped AI**
```bash
# Physical network isolation
sudo ip link set eth0 down  # Disconnect inference node

# Set up sneakernet queue
mkdir /mnt/usb/inference-queue-in
mkdir /mnt/usb/inference-queue-out
```

### **Month 9-10: Immutable Audit**
```bash
# OpenTimestamps for blockchain anchoring
ots stamp audit-log-2025-12-03.json

# WORM storage for logs
sudo mount -o remount,ro /var/log/audit
```

### **Month 11-12: Chaos Testing**
```bash
# Chaos Mesh attack simulation
kubectl apply -f chaos-experiments/pod-kill.yaml
kubectl apply -f chaos-experiments/network-partition.yaml
kubectl apply -f chaos-experiments/credential-leak-test.yaml
```

